description: This Chainlink VRF common Sakura purrs with a rating of 40, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 120, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, 5 for East, 5 for South, and 5 for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/10403-45550-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [120 Votes, Common]
